title: Chicago XXX (30)
description:
We&#039;ve arrived at the end of the albums -- I&#039;m not going to post simply compilations with no new material, it&#039;s a waste of space.  But I will be posting some Chicago videos and, after I attend a Chicago concert in a bit here, I will hopefully have a bootleg to post as well.

Contents of this album:



Feel (Hot Single Mix)

Caroline

Why Can&#039;t We

Love Will Come Back

Long Lost Friend

Hopefully by now somebody else in the world realizes that Chicago belongs in the rock-and-roll Hall of Fame.

Enjoy!
